org.acplt.oncrpc
Interface OncRpcRejectStatus

public interface OncRpcRejectStatus

A collection of constants used to describe why a remote procedure call message was rejected. This constants are used in OncRpcReplyMessage objects, which represent rejected messages if their OncRpcReplyMessage.replyStatus field has the value OncRpcReplyStatus.ONCRPC_MSG_DENIED.
